Crysis,Stats,provides,users,with,access,to,their,statistics,for,Crysis,a,multi,platform,first,person,shooter,video,game,Players,can,use,Crysis,Stats,to,view,their,progress,over,time,or,to,share,their,game,stats,with,others,The,Crysis,Stats,API,allows,developers,to,retrieve,game,statistics,from,the,website,for,integration,into,their,own,applications,It,should,be,noted,that,commercial,use,of,the,API,is,discouraged